title: Activism vs. "Digital Nomadism" (a Political Autobiography of sorts)
description: You want to make a positive difference in the world?  In many ways, it starts with having a fixed address.  This video offers some reflections on my own life, and the contrast between the type of activism that was possible for me at Toronto City Hall, and the strange fate of living from one airplane ticket to the next as an expatriate ("nomad") in Asia.
